<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨٧ سورة الأعلى]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الأعلى <span class="c2">(٨٧)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٧]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى <span class="c2">(١)</span> الَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّى <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَالَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدى <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَالَّذِي أَخْرَجَ الْمَرْعى <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَجَعَلَهُ غُثاءً أَحْوى <span class="c2">(٥)</span> سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلا تَنْسى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> إِلاَّ ما شاءَ اللَّهُ إِنَّهُ يَعْلَمُ الْجَهْرَ وَما يَخْفى <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>نزه اسم ربك الأعظم عما لا يليق به.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> الَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الَّذِي خَلَقَ كل شىء.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَسَوَّى فجعله مستوى الخلق.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> وَالَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدى:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالَّذِي قَدَّرَ لكل شىء ما يصلحه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَهَدى فهداه إليه.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> وَالَّذِي أَخْرَجَ الْمَرْعى:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أي الذي أخرج من الأرض ما ترعاه الدواب من صنوف النبات.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> فَجَعَلَهُ غُثاءً أَحْوى:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَجَعَلَهُ فصيره بعد الخضرة.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>غُثاءً يابسا.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَحْوى مسودا.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلا تَنْسى:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>سَنُقْرِئُكَ أي سنجعلك يا محمد صلّى الله عليه وسلم قارئا بإلهام منا.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>فَلا تَنْسى ما تحفظ.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> إِلَّا ما شاءَ اللَّهُ إِنَّهُ يَعْلَمُ الْجَهْرَ وَما يَخْفى:</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>إِلَّا ما شاءَ اللَّهُ أن تنساه.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>